   "TrashedCells" -> {"val = \
0.0;\nPrintTemporary[ProgressIndicator[val//Offload]];\nDo[val+=0.1; \
Pause[0.25], {10.0}];\n\"Hey\"", ".md\n## PrintTemporary\nWe added another \
missing feature `PrintTemporary`. It prints `expr` and then automatically \
removes it after the evaluation is finished", "values = \
{};\nMonitor[NIntegrate[Sqrt[x (1 - x)], {x, 0, 1}, \n  EvaluationMonitor :> \
(Pause[0.025]; AppendTo[values, x];)], \n Quiet@ListPlot[values]]", ".md\n## \
`Monitor` support\nWe added the missing `Monitor` symbol, which should help \
your to watch the intermediate results of your long computations:", ".md\n## \
Layout improvements\n- Chat window control buttons were misplaced on \
Windows/Linux machines\n"}|>, 
